We have full upstream support in order to package Ciao for Debian

It was downloaded from the ciao svn repository at clip.dia.fi.upm.es

Upstream Authors: Francisco Bueno, Daniel Cabeza, Manuel Carro,
                  Manuel Hermenegildo, Pedro Lopez, and German Puebla
                  and a lot of small contributors.

Some files are missing copyright headers, upstream is working on it.

contrib/ directory has some packages with different licences.

